title: Pytorch ResNeXt 32x8d
description: IntroductionThis is a simple fork of my previous kernel (https://www.kaggle.com/taindow/pytorch-efficientnet-b0), except here we make use of ResNeXt and "weakly supervised pre-training" as opposed to EfficientNet. See https://github.com/facebookresearch/WSL-Images for model information. Note due to the number of parameters a single sweep of the data will take approx. 4-5h.
